snippet.title: Shotgun Knight - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2341240/Shotgun_Knight/

Embark on an impossible climb with nothing but yourself and a shotgun to propel yourself upwards while falling losing all your progress countless times.

Devlog series coming soon!
